title: Episode 180: The Patdown Crackdown Recap Live with Donnell Rawlings
description:
The day after the Patdown Podcast Crackdown, everyone was a little rough. For example, one girl got lost and tried to steal a wheelchair, and another guy got friend-zoned live on the podcast. Joining us live on the stage is comedian Donnell Rawlings.
